---
title: South-of-the-Border Beef Taco Salad with Pickled Onion, Avocado Dressing & Lime Crema
description: Looking to spice up dinner? Let’s give ‘em something to taco-bout! This taco salad’s got all the textures and flavors you’d expect from your fave Tex-Mex joint: crisp lettuce, spiced beef, onion, and tomato. But, it’s also got a little something extra. We’re talking pickled red onion, a zesty avocado dressing, lime crema, and blue corn tortilla chips for dipping, scooping, and crushing over top. Going the extra mile is just our style!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/south-of-the-border-beef-taco-salad-f6d6adab.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/south-of-the-border-beef-taco-salad-6239d652da06ab7187561c16-b34f3564.pdf
